snippet.title: Johnny Depp Sues Amber Heard For $50 Million
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp Sues Amber Heard For $50 Million
Subscribe Here 👉 http://bit.ly/2xB5CqA
Recent Uploads: https://bit.ly/37WEaXF

Amber Heard has failed to have Johnny Depp's 50 million dollar lawsuit thrown out after a judge deems Johnny's loss in the UK as not being enough to determine a verdict. This is really great news considering the UK trial was just about his defamation from the Sun newspaper.
